Add new methods to Game:

**`addNPC()`**:
```js
addNPC() {
  const id = this.nextPlayerId++;
  const name = NPC_NAMES[this.npcNameIndex % NPC_NAMES.length];
  this.npcNameIndex++;
  const npc = createNPC(id, name);
  this.spawnPlayer(npc);
  this.players.set(id, npc);
  this.npcIds.add(id);
  return id;
}
```

**`removeNPC(id)`**:
```js
removeNPC(id) {
  this.players.delete(id);
  this.npcIds.delete(id);
  this.spectators.delete(id);
}
```

**`removeAllNPCs()`**:
```js
removeAllNPCs() {
  for (const id of this.npcIds) {
    this.players.delete(id);
    this.spectators.delete(id);
  }
  this.npcIds.clear();
}
```

**`getRealPlayerCount()`**: Count players that are NOT NPCs and NOT spectators.
```js
getRealPlayerCount() {
  let count = 0;
  for (const p of this.players.values()) {
    if (!this.npcIds.has(p.id) && !this.spectators.has(p.id)) count++;
  }
  return count;
}
```

**`fillWithNPCs()`**: Called in tickLobby. Ensures enough players to start.
```js
fillWithNPCs() {
  const realCount = this.getRealPlayerCount();
  if (realCount >= MIN_REAL_PLAYERS_FOR_NO_BOTS) {
    // Enough real players — remove any existing NPCs
    this.removeAllNPCs();
    return;
  }
  // Target: fill up to MAX_NPC_COUNT + realCount, but at least MIN_PLAYERS_TO_START total
  const targetTotal = Math.max(MIN_PLAYERS_TO_START, realCount + MAX_NPC_COUNT);
  const currentTotal = this.getNonSpectatorPlayers().length;

  // Add NPCs if needed
  while (this.getNonSpectatorPlayers().length < targetTotal) {
    this.addNPC();
  }

  // Remove excess NPCs if real players joined
  while (this.getNonSpectatorPlayers().length > targetTotal && this.npcIds.size > 0) {
    const lastNpcId = [...this.npcIds].pop();
    this.removeNPC(lastNpcId);
  }
}
```

**`tickNPCs(dt)`**: Run AI for each NPC during active game.
```js
tickNPCs(dt) {
  for (const id of this.npcIds) {
    const npc = this.players.get(id);
    if (!npc || !npc.alive) continue;

    const aiCtx = {
      players: this.players,
      npcIds: this.npcIds,
      ringVertices: this.ringVertices,
      arenaVertices: this.arenaVertices,
      arenaCentroid: this.arenaCentroid,
      pointInPolygon: pointInConvexPolygon,
      spectators: this.spectators,
    };
    const result = updateNPCAI(npc, aiCtx);
    if (result && result.shoot) {
      this.tryShoot(npc);
    }
  }
}
```

**Modify `tickLobby(now)`**: Add `this.fillWithNPCs()` call at the beginning.

**Modify `tickActive(dt, now)`**: Add `this.tickNPCs(dt)` BEFORE the player movement loop.

**Modify `resetForNextRound()`**: Call `this.removeAllNPCs()` at the beginning, before resetting players. Then the existing loop only handles real players.

**Modify `getState(forPlayerId)`**: Add `isNPC: this.npcIds.has(p.id)` to each player object in the serialized state.

**Modify `checkLobbyStart()`** (inside `tickLobby`): The existing logic checks `getAlivePlayers().length >= MIN_PLAYERS_TO_START`. Since NPCs are counted as alive players, this works naturally.

